property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
WITH "CTE_Sort_CustomerDocCancel" AS (
    SELECT 
        "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"                                                     AS "ID",
        "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID"                                                      AS "CustomerInvoice",
        "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Time"                                                            AS "Time",
        "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationType"                                                   AS "CancellationType",
        "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."ChangedBy"                                                       AS "ExecutedBy",
        "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."ExecutionType"                                                   AS "ExecutionType",
        "CustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType"                                                         AS "CustomerInvoiceType",
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"  
             ORDER BY "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Time" ASC)                                         AS "rn"
    FROM "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
        LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"  
            ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."ObjectID" 
        LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"  
            ON "CustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID"          
    WHERE "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Attribute" = 'Cancellation'
        AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT 
    'CancelCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."ID"                          AS "ID",
    "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."CustomerInvoice"                                                AS "CustomerInvoice",
    "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."Time"                                                           AS "Time",
    "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."CancellationType"                                               AS "CancellationType",
    "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."ExecutedBy"                                                     AS "ExecutedBy",
    "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."ExecutionType"                                                  AS "ExecutionType",
    "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."CustomerInvoiceType"                                            AS "CustomerInvoiceType"
FROM "CTE_Sort_CustomerDocCancel" AS "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"        
WHERE "Sort_CustomerDocCancel"."rn" = 1

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'CancelCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"                AS "ID",
    "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID"                                                                    AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
FROM "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."ObjectID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"  
        ON "CustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID"
WHERE "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Attribute" = 'Cancellation'
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"  IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
    'CancelCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"                AS "ID",
    "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"."ID"                                                            AS "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"
FROM "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."ObjectID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"  
        ON "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"
WHERE "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Attribute" = 'Cancellation'
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"  IS NOT NULL
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine"."PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine" IS NOT NULL
    AND "PreviousCustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
    'CancelCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"                AS "ID",
    "CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"."SalesOrderScheduleLines_ID"                   AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
FROM "r_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."ObjectID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"  
        ON "CustomerInvoice"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID"
WHERE "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Attribute" = 'Cancellation'
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine_Changes"."OperationID"  IS NOT NULL
